    <item>
      <title>由于美联储信号关注我们的Outlook，EM货币保持稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/emerging-market-currencies-drop-as-selloff-spreads-from-turkey</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美联储决定保持利率不变并对美国经济前景和政策不确定性表现出担忧之后，新兴市场货币的指数几乎没有改变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/emerging-market-currencies-drop-as-selloff-spreads-from-turkey</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 09:37:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在看好美国数据浮标摇摇欲坠的需求前景之后，石油边缘上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-19</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国政府的报告减轻了对近期需求破坏的担忧之后，石油也越来越好，即使美联储预测减缓了经济增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-19</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Mar 2025 23:22:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
